description: Testing, Logging, Monitoring, and API Standards
globs: ["src/**/*.ts"]
alwaysApply: true
---

## 🧪 Testing
- Use Jest for unit/integration/e2e tests.
- Mock dependencies using TestingModule.
- Include tests in CI pipeline.

## 📊 Logging & Monitoring
- Use performant logger (nestjs-pino, winston, or pino).
- Log structured JSON, request timing, and error details.
- Expose metrics (Prometheus) via interceptor/middleware.
- Integrate Sentry or APM in production.


## 🔖 Versioning & Documentation
- Version APIs (e.g., `/api/v1/`).
- Use Swagger/OpenAPI decorators for docs.
- Define clear DTOs and error responses.
- Maintain consistent naming conventions.
